description: Demolition of existing buildings on site and the erection of a part 6-storey building (along Queensbridge Road frontage), Part 4-storey building (corner Holly Street and Forest Road) and 3-storey buildings (along entire Forest Road frontage and on Holly Street) and 2 storey terraced dwellings to new internal one-way street linking Holly Street and Queensbridge Road. Development to contain 151 residential units consisting of 48 dwelling houses, 101 flats/maisonettes and 2 studios providing 41 x 1-bedroom units, 60 x 2-bedroom units, 34 x 3-bedroom units, 16 x 4-bedroom units with 71 parking spaces (67 on-street spaces and 4 on-site disabled parking spaces).
